sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway / Envoy<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as Endpoint Picker (EPP)<br/>ext-proc gRPC
    participant FC as Flow Control<br/>(Priority/Fairness)
    participant Sched as Scheduler<br/>(Filter→Score→Pick)
    participant Pool as InferencePool CR
    participant Prefill as Prefill Worker<br/>8000/TCP
    participant NIXL as NIXL KV Transfer<br/>5600/TCP RDMA
    participant Decode as Decode Worker<br/>8200/TCP
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9002/9090

    Note over Client,Decode: Standard Inference Flow (Non-Disaggregated)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>OpenAI-compatible API
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc gRPC<br/>(FULL_DUPLEX_STREAMED)
    EPP->>FC: Parse request (OpenAI format)
    FC->>FC: Check priority band<br/>(Premium/Standard/Best-Effort)
    FC->>FC: Fairness check<br/>(x-gateway-inference-fairness-id)
    FC->>Sched: Dispatch request
    Sched->>Pool: Get endpoints<br/>(label selector)
    Pool-->>Sched: Available endpoints
    Sched->>Sched: Filter: KV cache, queue depth
    Sched->>Sched: Score: prefix-cache, load, LoRA
    Sched->>Sched: Pick: max-score / weighted-random
    Sched-->>EPP: Selected endpoint
    EPP-->>Gateway: Endpoint address
    Gateway->>Decode: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
    Decode-->>Gateway: Streaming response (SSE)
    Gateway-->>Client: Streaming response

    Note over Client,Decode: Prefill/Decode Disaggregation Flow
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc gRPC
    EPP->>Sched: Route via disagg-profile-handler
    Sched->>Sched: Select P & D worker pair
    Sched-->>EPP: Prefill + Decode endpoints
    EPP-->>Gateway: Prefill endpoint
    Gateway->>Prefill: Forward (max_tokens=1)<br/>HTTP/8000
    Prefill->>NIXL: KV cache transfer<br/>GPUDirect RDMA/5600
    NIXL->>Decode: KV blocks transferred
    Decode-->>Gateway: Streaming response<br/>HTTP/8200
    Gateway-->>Client: Streaming response

    Note over Sched,Prom: Background: Metrics Collection
    loop Every polling interval
        Prom-->>Sched: TotalQueuedRequests<br/>TotalRunningRequests<br/>KVCacheUtilization
    end

    Note over Client,Decode: Precise Prefix Cache-Aware Flow
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc gRPC
    EPP->>Sched: Route with prefix scoring
    Note right of Sched: ZMQ subscriber receives<br/>real-time KV block events<br/>from vLLM (port 5556)
    Sched->>Sched: Score: precise-prefix-cache-scorer<br/>(highest block residency)
    Sched-->>EPP: Best cache-matched endpoint
    EPP-->>Gateway: Endpoint address
    Gateway->>Decode: Forward request
    Decode-->>Client: Response (cache hit = faster TTFT)
